Followed users is an English Wikipedia tool running on Toolserver
that allows you to keep a list of users that you follow, similar to a
watchlist, and lists the most recent edit by each user. For more, see:

http://toolserver.org/~dcoetzee/followedusers/

The PHP source for Followed users is available under the Simplified
(2-clause) BSD License. It must be on Toolserver to run.
